      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-home-price-slump-accelerates-despite-more-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于国家最有力的房地产市场刺激措施需要时间来恢复需求，中国5月份房价下跌速度加快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/china-home-price-slump-accelerates-despite-more-stimulus</guid>
